com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity.GWObject
      • com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity.Contact
        • com.guidewire.ab.webservices.entity.Person
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PersonVendor, UserContact

    public class Person
extends Contact
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a person as a primary subtype of Contact.

    Person extends Contact with additional information about individuals that is not applicable to companies or places.
